00:39:32,090 --> 00:39:34,416
A meat hook? A meat hook?

634
00:39:34,551 --> 00:39:37,007
OK. I'll go first.

635
00:39:38,055 --> 00:39:41,424
- I'm angry. I'm telling you, I'm angry.
