00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:12,589
So Danny and Tina, they run.

639
00:40:14,091 --> 00:40:19,678
What's he gonna do? Now he is not
only scared. The man is pissed off.

640
00:40:19,805 --> 00:40:23,470
- Sure. Because he didn't do anything.
